static void vteprec_physical_switch_parse_tunnels ( struct ovsdb_idl_row *  row_,
const struct ovsdb_datum *  datum 
)
static
5596 {
5597  struct vteprec_physical_switch *row = vteprec_physical_switch_cast(row_);
5598  size_t i;
5599 
5600  ovs_assert(inited);
5601  row->tunnels = NULL;
5602  row->n_tunnels = 0;
5603  for (i = 0; i < datum->n; i++) {
5604  struct vteprec_tunnel *keyRow = vteprec_tunnel_cast(ovsdb_idl_get_row_arc(row_, &vteprec_table_classes[VTEPREC_TABLE_TUNNEL], &datum->keys[i].uuid));
5605  if (keyRow) {
5606  if (!row->n_tunnels) {
5607  row->tunnels = xmalloc(datum->n * sizeof *row->tunnels);
5608  }
5609  row->tunnels[row->n_tunnels] = keyRow;
5610  row->n_tunnels++;
5611  }
5612  }
5613 }

6965  struct smap_node *node;
6966  size_t i;
6967

6969  datum.keys = xmalloc(datum.n * sizeof *datum.keys);

7069
